{"tid":1564169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淘大男教師影大頭指罵街坊 學校稱中肯  教聯會稱勇於發聲","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:36:27.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"72d5a14ce50c899d653952816101bea84f4389f8","tid":1564169,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"淘大商場街坊昨晚（11日）聚集齊唱《願榮光歸香港》，有中年男子帶同3名年幼子女到場，突然唱國歌和近攝他人容貌，挑釁和指罵街坊，不但令其子女受驚，更與人爭執打鬥受傷。該涉事男子被網民發現為東華三院王余家潔紀念小學李姓教師。校方今發通告稱該老師教學時持平中肯，上述事件發生在公餘時間，「純屬個人事件」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東華三院回覆《蘋果》時，未有正面回應會否跟進上述個案，僅稱「由於警方現正了解事件的背景及過程，學校不會就此事作任何評論。」惟親中的教聯會卻讚揚該男教師「無懼群眾壓力高唱國歌，勇於發聲，撥亂反正」，起身教作用，值得肯定，向他致以深切慰問和崇高敬意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10158051212117448?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10158051212117448%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmJS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=78079c14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10158051212117448?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5799ddc1f5bdbc076afd56f69c61c348b629e51f","tid":1564169,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80beccd5cbf703629d8c26d55c28175e30883e09","tid":1564169,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\